name: Ancient Plant Pod
description:
A gift from Saturn's city on Enceladus, sent to the people of Mars. A pod containing ancient decorative plant life for propagation on the red planet. These organisms originally grew naturally on the surface of planet Earth, over three centuries ago. The Enceladens presented this gift as a token of gratitude, for the recently authorized “Frozen Water for Carbon” trade deal.

Original visual, writing, and music.
